WEBVTT

00:04.104 --> 00:08.871
l always say there's
three kinds of people in the world.

00:08.942 --> 00:12.434
Them who make things happen,
them who watch things happen,

00:12.512 --> 00:16.277
and them who wonder what happened.

00:16.349 --> 00:18.544
l made things happen.

00:18.618 --> 00:20.711
The wrong things.

00:20.787 --> 00:24.746
l caused pain to anyone who came near me.

00:24.824 --> 00:29.318
This tattoo,
it used to be my badge of honor.

00:29.396 --> 00:34.800
But l'm a different man
since l joined group. A better man.

00:34.868 --> 00:38.565
l never thought words like that
would come out of my mouth.

00:38.671 --> 00:44.803
lt's all because of the help and the love
that l found in this room.

00:45.912 --> 00:51.680
- You're new here. ls it Ed?
- Yeah, l'm new to this BS.

00:51.751 --> 00:53.844
Why do you think it's BS?

00:53.920 --> 00:57.651
Listen, l turned my life around.
A lot of us here have.

00:57.724 --> 01:00.386
Our kind of lives go one way.

01:00.493 --> 01:05.055
And you can't change, any more than
you can undo the crimes you've done.

01:05.165 --> 01:08.862
l feel sorry for you.

01:09.335 --> 01:13.931
Don't feel sorry.
You're going to hell just like l am.

01:17.010 --> 01:19.843
Why are you here, Ed?

01:19.913 --> 01:23.940
l drove Victor. He knows l'm right.

01:24.050 --> 01:28.851
- Victor's been doin' good.
- Yeah. Just look at him.

01:34.928 --> 01:37.761
Victor, you wanna talk about it?

01:41.734 --> 01:44.794
l've just been having bad dreams.

01:44.904 --> 01:46.963
Really bad dreams.

01:49.109 --> 01:51.703
What kind of dreams?

01:55.782 --> 01:59.309
Seeing people skinned alive.

02:05.592 --> 02:07.924
lt's a hard road, Victor.

02:07.994 --> 02:12.761
lt's a shock to the system, changing
the way we think, taking charge of our lives.

02:12.832 --> 02:18.327
We're all afraid,
and that fear preys on us night and day.

02:19.038 --> 02:21.802
ln our minds and in our dreams.

02:28.615 --> 02:30.879
You ever get enough of that crap?

02:30.984 --> 02:35.944
The ''shock to the system'' crap?
This ''fear preying on us night and day'' crap?

02:36.022 --> 02:39.753
Those boys are afraid of one thing:
themselves, their true natures.

02:39.826 --> 02:42.989
- You know what l'm saying, Victor?
- Sorta.

02:43.062 --> 02:46.498
What do you mean?
Don't tell me that bull does you any good.

02:46.566 --> 02:50.332
And don't tell me you feel any better
about yourself coming here,

02:50.403 --> 02:53.861
that it makes these nightmares go away.

02:58.645 --> 03:00.704
No, it don't.

